<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>Aur(elius) Fl(avius) Elpidephoros constructed the sarcophagus and the burial places below it, in which has been buried Aur(elius) <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> Fl(avius) Epitynchanon, his father,  and will be buried Aur(elia) Fl(avia) Elpis his mother, and Aur(elia) Aphrodeisia (daughter of) Tatianos the (son of) Tatianos the (son of) Alexandros the (son of) Krokos, his wife and M(arcus) Aur(elius) Epitynchanon his [?son . . . .] and Elpidephoros himself will also be buried, but no-one else <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></p>
</div>
